```shell

```

### Impact

Major – Severely degrades functionality; workaround is difficult or unavailable.

### Environment

OS: Windows

Toolchain: arm-zephyr-eabi-gcc.exe (Zephyr SDK 0.17.4) 12.2.0

Zephyr Version: 4.3.99
Revision:  #https://github.com/zephyrproject-rtos/zephyr/commit/4f3478391a3c5e555dcd629f9e829378c17b0d62

